+ "free time on media" list now working
+ added page with instructions how to setup phpVideoPro
+ added setup script for database
+ adding a new entry is now possible! So this fine piece of software should now
  be useful even for people other than me :)
* Going to feature freeze (now the product has all its "main functions" and can,
  as mentioned above, be used by "the public") and check for bugs (guess I'll
  have to force myself to this step - since there are some functions I am dying
  to implement ;). If no bugs are found within the next days (or the ones found
  are fixed), version number will change to 0.1.0 as first public beta (wow!)

